Date: 1997-07-17

Title: Phase of a chiral determinant and global SU(2) anomaly

Authors: A. A. Slavnov

Comments: 6 pages, Latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B415 (1997) 390-394

A representation for the phase of a chiral determinant in terms of a pathintegral of a local action is constructed. This representation is used tomodify the action of chiral SU(2) fermions removing the global anomaly.